DNSSEC-related code is now enclosed within #ifdef SUPPORT_DNSSEC ... #endif
constructs.  SUPPORT_DNSSEC is defined when the --enable-dnssec-support
option is specified while configuring libspf2-1.2.5.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
